WEBVTT

1
00:10:19.340 --> 00:10:21.830 
真是给我造成大大的不便
is just so inconvenient for me.

2
00:10:23.970 --> 00:10:26.080 
好的  现在我们有个真的大问题了
Okay, now we have a real situation.

3
00:10:26.180 --> 00:10:28.410 
你打人了  靠  麦克斯
You hit someone. Damn it, Max.

4
00:10:28.410 --> 00:10:30.100 
跟我无关  是苏菲
It's not about me. It's Sophie.

5
00:10:30.100 --> 00:10:31.330 
她的婚纱从波兰寄到了
Her gown arrived from Poland

6
00:10:31.330 --> 00:10:33.710 
现在被卡在外面海关那里
and it's stuck in customs out here.

7
00:10:34.280 --> 00:10:35.800 
我的婚纱
My gown!

8
00:10:35.800 --> 00:10:37.550 
我漂漂的婚纱
My beautiful gown!

9
00:10:37.550 --> 00:10:40.770 
天啊  我的婚纱
Oh, my God! My gown!

10
00:10:40.770 --> 00:10:42.890 
看来她很不开心啊
Wow. She is really upset.

11
00:10:42.890 --> 00:10:43.880 
是非常不开心
Really upset,

12
00:10:43.880 --> 00:10:46.050 
没按免提都已经这音量了
'cause this isn't even on speaker.

13
00:10:48.210 --> 00:10:51.260 
的确很棘手  但往好的一面看
Yes, it's awful, but look on the bright side.

